System of Management Courses

1. User
1.1. Registration Form (It will create a username and password).
1.2. Screen exclusively for the user to view your history.
1.3. Certificate Online

2. Administrator
2.1. Insert, edit and update courses.
2.2. Screens to display the acting courses, conducted and
future.
2.3. Manage users.

3. Public page with the courses available and the link
registration by sending a login screen aiming to accomplish
enrollment.

